info.name: Dark RuTracker .ORG .NET без реверса
info.description:
A dark theme for RuTracker.org , RuTracker.net etc. Dominated by orange and red colors.
Initially based on http://userstyles.org/styles/4407/dark-theme-for-phpbb-v2-subsilver-site

Donate:
WMR: R309863884007 
WMZ: Z110567914520 

- No ads, banners, userbars
- Colortheme
- Theme graphics (incl. logo)
- Status icons
- Some smilies
